title: Neptune
occurrences: This August Voyager 2 will pass within 3,000 miles of the planet Neptune.
Using its television cameras, Voyager 2 will send back pictures of Neptune...
Voyager 2 passed over the cold blue clouds of Neptune tonight,
As Voyager 2 approached Neptune at a speed of 38,000 miles an hour,
in Neptune's great dark spots, a storm system the size of earth.
